{"tid":999031,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"火影入面有邊啲角色有機會係處男/處女？","createTime":"2019-01-28T11:57:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-04T14:24:14.000Z","uid":64694,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"8c5d55c94c6349acfcdd1eb51b834dc6b451c6ee","tid":999031,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T11:57:30.000Z","msg":"<strong>宇智波斑/內輪摩馱羅</strong><br />\n俾初代火影背後一插，之後用伊邪那岐返生，之後落咗地底直到老年之後開輪迴眼<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SNkEdhL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSNkEdhL.jpg&h=f6e5ea3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kvZ5ThM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkvZ5ThM.png&h=9b7a2cda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PqPBfv7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPqPBfv7.jpg&h=77c0b46a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>旗木卡卡西/畑鹿驚</strong><br />\n做咗火影之後都冇結婚<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/puON6Eq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpuON6Eq.jpg&h=4fd1f75b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>邁特凱/真井賀意</strong><br />\n一腳踢爆咗斑之後，最後同卡卡西一齊飲嘢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fmYqTkA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfmYqTkA.jpg&h=7dfedcf1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MdroE0A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMdroE0A.jpg&h=d57f306a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>天天</strong><br />\n寧次死咗，冇結婚<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yj14psT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyj14psT.png&h=a18289fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tss3E1V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftss3E1V.jpg&h=918f04e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kKLHVAg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkKLHVAg.jpg&h=32306426&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZHRcymW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZHRcymW.jpg&h=a6e9e1cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n重有冇？"},{"pid":"d893e4149d9cc30db8232661aa61017e94f5d5dd","tid":999031,"uid":3852,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T11:59:48.000Z","msg":"鼬"},{"pid":"b52e28ce1e51a4a63e4c1a9fb30d411feaad5dcd","tid":999031,"uid":91982,"like":16,"dislike":3,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T12:02:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6b54d946b6de0c6e07f75d90aa81f17896ba58b9","tid":999031,"uid":38526,"like":57,"dislike":1,"score":56,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T12:04:50.000Z","msg":"想知小李係咪單性繁殖小小李出黎"},{"pid":"24977611cfe7279859855d53ff8b4ea3b22a9eb6","tid":999031,"uid":64694,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"d893e4149d9cc30db8232661aa61017e94f5d5dd","tid":999031,"uid":3852,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T11:59:48.000Z","msg":"鼬"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T12:10:18.000Z","msg":"好想知曉入面班人見到小南有咩睇法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"369051bed899ab5035a66f27d44cb520dbb26257","tid":999031,"uid":67896,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T12:13:36.000Z","msg":"油女志乃<br />\n邊個想玩蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a66f5643e62d04196fddfc81ea7fd887f7c90ac","tid":999031,"uid":29112,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"24977611cfe7279859855d53ff8b4ea3b22a9eb6","tid":999031,"uid":64694,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"d893e4149d9cc30db8232661aa61017e94f5d5dd","tid":999031,"uid":3852,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T11:59:48.000Z","msg":"鼬"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T12:10:18.000Z","msg":"好想知曉入面班人見到小南有咩睇法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T12:15:58